data.description: Well maintained home with a spacious open concept floor plan includes an extra large owner's suite, large secondary bedrooms and laundry room upstairs, mudroom off of the garage, and an additional gathering room downstairs.  Upgraded features such as tray ceilings, hardwoods downstairs and on the staircase, gas fireplace, stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, tile shower in the primary ensuite, large closets, plus a large fenced in backyard with an extended back deck. All appliances, including washer/dryer and refrigerator, remain.  HOA amenities include a community pool, walking trail, and a playground. Located in the desirable and convenient Fairway Farms - this one is a must see!
